When you use `moment()` constructor, it creates a moment instance representing the current time. So instead use [parsing][1] to create an instance with the time you are providing.

Then format that instance as using format method providing the date format as the first and only parameter.

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-js --&gt;

